      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but isn't \"well-designed nationalism\" kinda an oxymoron? if you're prioritizing everyone equally, isn't that just civic patriotism rather than actual nationalism? it feels like you're trying to sanitize it to make it sound more acceptable, even though history shows it almost always results in some kind of exclusion or conflict.",
